title: The Wire - Season 4 Complete High Quality
description:
ok.
so it took me a very long time to find a high quality set of the wire season 4 episodes, and here it finally is. it was tucked away pretty well in rar files with french subs included, so i thought i'd make it a little more obvious for everyone else. all credit goes to original uploader FBX. french subs are not hardcoded, simply removed, and i've added in the english subtitles in the form of srt files.

season 4 presents an insight into the school systems and continues on with some political themes also. don't worry, no more town hall meetings or city hall council. in my opinion, the best season since the first.

all tried and tested on my dvd player, works fine.
anyways, all thanks to FBX and everyone who seeds.
and don't bitch at me if it doesn't work out, the files are quality, i'm just new at this.
